               <bibl>ms Damas, Patriarcat syrien orthodoxe, cod. 12/17 (olim ms Dayr az-Za‘faran, cod. parch. 18 (Dolabany)), f. 114-116v</bibl>
            </note>
            <note xml:lang="" type="modernTranslation" source="#bib221-1">
